ISLAMABAD, Nov 17 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi on Friday appointed Dr Shahzad Ali Khan as the Vice Chancellor of Health Services Academy, Islamabad.
The president made the said appointment in exercise of the powers under section 12 (1) of Health Services Academy Act 2018, a President House press release said.
